11. COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID
------------------------------------------------------------

✗ plt.show(img)          -> plt.show() takes NO arguments
✗ requests.get(url).astext -> correct is .text
✗ cv2.addWeighted(img, contrast=1.5, ...)  -> NO keyword args, all positional
✗ cv2.resize(img, (height, width))  -> it's (WIDTH, height) not (height, width)
✗ plt.imshow(cv2.imread(img))       -> BGR colors will be wrong, convert first!

